European Union Banks May Raise 200 Billion Pounds, BBC Reports

-- B y   M a r i a   E r m a k o v a
-- 
2011-10-13T08:19:28Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-13/european-union-banks-may-raise-200-billion-pounds-bbc-reports.html
Euro-region banks may be forced to
raise about 200 billion pounds of additional capital, if the
European Union governments accept recommendations by the
European Banking Authority, the British Broadcasting Corp.
reported on its website, without citing anyone.  To contact the reporter on this story:
